inefficient na loss-making state-owned biashara ( SOEs ) kuwa shida ya msingi beneficiaries rasmi ya sera ya uchumi , iliiweka hai kwenye drip-feed ruzuku ya serikali na bei rahisi kutoka state-owned mikopo ya benki . 
